# AI Resume & Mock Interviewer (HR-Tech)

## Problem Statement
Many job applicants do not understand why their resumes get rejected.
Traditional ATS systems act like black boxes and provide no feedback.

## Solution
This project is an AI-powered Resume Analyzer and Mock Interviewer.
It explains resume gaps clearly and helps users practice interview questions
based on their missing or weak skills.

## Key Features
- Resume vs Job Description matching
- Match score generation
- Missing skills and keyword detection
- Role-specific interview question generation.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React
- Backend: Python (FastAPI)
- AI: Large Language Model (Prompt Engineering)
- Output Format: Structured JSON

## Project Workflow (High Level)
1. User uploads resume and job description
2. AI analyzes both and returns structured feedback
3. User practices interview questions

## Learning Focus (Hackathon Goal)
- Prompt chaining
- Few-shot prompting
- Structured JSON outputs
- Agentic AI workflows